mes, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert de Carlyle was born in 1139, in Annan, Dumfriesshire, Scotland, United Kingdom as the son of Odard de Karliolo. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"1139–":"1139–Surnud","1139–Male":"1139–Surnud","1160–1213":"1160–1213","–1140":"–1140","1139":"1139","1213":"1213","1140":"1140","1160":"1160","Hoddon Castle, Annan, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Annan, Dumfriesshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1139–":"1139–Kuollut","1139–Male":"1139–Kuollut","1160–1213":"1160–1213","–1140":"–1140","1139":"1139","1213":"1213","1140":"1140","1160":"1160","Hoddon Castle, Annan, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Annan, Dumfriesshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1139–":"1139–Décédé","1139–Male":"1139–Décédé","1160–1213":"1160–1213","–1140":"–1140","1139":"1139","1213":"1213","1140":"1140","1160":"1160","Hoddon Castle, Annan, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Annan, Dumfriesshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Robert de Carlyle est né en 1139, à Annan, Dumfriesshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni, fils de Odard de Karliolo. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1139–":"1139–Verstorben","1139–Male":"1139–Verstorben","1160–1213":"1160–1213","–1140":"–1140","1139":"1139","1213":"1213","1140":"1140","1160":"1160","Hoddon Castle, Annan, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Annan, Dumfriesshire, Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Robert de Carlyle wurde 1139 in Annan, Dumfriesshire, Schottland, United Kingdom, als Sohn von Odard de Karliolo geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1139–":"1139–Desede","1139–Male":"1139–Desede","1160–1213":"1160–1213","–1140":"–1140","1139":"1139","1213":"1213","1140":"1140","1160":"1160","Hoddon Castle, Annan, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Annan, Dumfriesshire, Ecosse, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1139–":"1139–elhunyt","1139–Male":"1139–elhunyt","1160–1213":"1160–1213","–1140":"–1140","1139":"1139","1213":"1213","1140":"1140","1160":"1160","Hoddon Castle, Annan, Dumfriesshire, Scotland":"Annan, Dumfriess